                    <Value>The Timesheet Detail Report provides a detailed view of work logged on various projects. It includes the project name, date, module, task, and specific project activities along with their details. The report also shows who created the entry and the actual hours spent. This helps track time and activity Status across different tasks and modules.</Value>
